  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK424">
<l>eṇporuḷa vākac celaccollit tāṉpiṟarvāy</l>
<l>nuṇporuḷ kāṇpa taṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To speak so as that the meaning may easily enter the mind of the hearer, and to discern the subtlest thought which may lie hidden in the words of others, this is wisdom.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
